                {
                    "lang": "en",
                    "value": "Two questionnaires were completed at the maternity ward: one by the mother regarding her age, height, and weight before pregnancy; their professional status, education level, marital status and infant milk feeding during the first days in the maternity ward. The other questionnaire was completed by the midwife regarding medical and obstetric history, date of birth, and pregnancy outcome."
                }
